@startuml TestHaters_ctflow
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "VS Code" as VSCode {
  rectangle "CTFLOW Extension" as Extension {
    rectangle "Webview UI (React)" as Webview
  }
}

rectangle "Cypress" as Cypress #palegreen
rectangle "Firebase" as Firebase #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> Webview : Drag-and-drop test flow creation

Webview <--> Extension : VS Code API communication
Extension --> Cypress : Execute generated test code
Extension <--> Firebase : Real-time collaboration (potential)

Webview --> Webview : Compile visual flow to Cypress code
Webview --> Webview : Manage custom nodes
Webview --> Webview : Persist test flows (.ctflow files)

Cypress --> Cypress : Run automated tests
@enduml